PN,30601
SC,0001
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773209293
OL,3,CYoung mother died from sepsis after
OL,4,Cbeing prescribed wrong antibiotics
OL,6,FA young mother died from sepsis
OL,7,Fcontributed to by NHS neglect after
OL,8,Fshe was given the wrong antibiotics, a
OL,9,Fcoroner has ruled.
OL,11,FAleisha Rochester, 33, a bank cashier
OL,12,Ffrom Croydon, south London, died two
OL,13,Fweeks after undergoing a routine
OL,14,Fprocedure to remove an abscess from
OL,15,Fher left armpit.
OL,17,FShe had sought medical help several
OL,18,Ftimes for her worsening condition and
OL,19,Fbeen prescribed antibiotics but not
OL,20,Fones that could tackle the bacteria
OL,21,Fcausing her infection.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773209293
OL,3,CYoung mother died from sepsis after
OL,4,Cbeing prescribed wrong antibiotics
OL,6,FStaff at St Epsom and St Helier
OL,7,FUniversity Hospitals also did not
OL,8,Ffollow the NHS trust's own guidelines
OL,9,Fon administering antibiotics,
OL,10,Fassistant coroner Sian Reeves said.
OL,12,FThe trust has apologised.
OL,14,FDuring an inquest in December, Ms
OL,15,FReeves ruled that Ms Rochester's death
OL,16,Fhad been contributed to by neglect and
OL,17,Fshe would most likely have lived if
OL,18,Fgiven the right antibiotics in time.
OL,20,FMs Rochester left behind a son,
OL,21,FXavier, now aged eight.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773209293
OL,3,CYoung mother died from sepsis after
OL,4,Cbeing prescribed wrong antibiotics
OL,6,FRecording her verdict, Ms Reeves said
OL,7,FMs Rochester suffered from the
OL,8,Fcondition hidradenitis suppurativa,
OL,9,Fwhich causes abscesses on the skin.
OL,11,FShe had undergone a routine day
OL,12,Fprocedure at St Thomas' Hospital on
OL,13,FAugust 5 2023 to remove abscesses from
OL,14,Fher left armpit and groin.
OL,16,F"At some point after the 10th of
OL,17,FAugust, she became unwell and the
OL,18,Fwound to her left armpit became
OL,19,Finfected," Ms Reeves said.
OL,26,@xD@AOU{D@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773209293
OL,3,CYoung mother died from sepsis after
OL,4,Cbeing prescribed wrong antibiotics
OL,6,F"She went to an out-of-hours GP
OL,7,Fappointment on the 13th of August
OL,8,Fwhere she was prescribed a course of
OL,9,Fpenicillin-based antibiotic.
OL,11,F"On the same day, she went to the A&E
OL,12,Fat Croydon University Hospital, where
OL,13,Fdoctors said she'd got a wound
OL,14,Finfection and discharged her home with
OL,15,Fa plan to continue the antibiotics.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773209293
OL,3,CYoung mother died from sepsis after
OL,4,Cbeing prescribed wrong antibiotics
OL,6,F"On the evening of the 14th of August,
OL,7,Fshe went to the A&E department at St
OL,8,FHelier hospital. She had a wound
OL,9,Finfection to her left armpit and was
OL,10,Fadministered a dose of flucloxacillin
OL,11,F(antibiotic) intravenously, and then
OL,12,Fwas sent home with a plan to return
OL,13,Fthe next day."
OL,15,FMs Rochester went back to hospital the
OL,16,Fnext morning and was seen by a junior
OL,17,Fdoctor and senior house officer,
OL,18,Ffollowed by a specialist.
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773209293
OL,3,CYoung mother died from sepsis after
OL,4,Cbeing prescribed wrong antibiotics
OL,6,F"Antibiotics were prescribed but were
OL,7,Fnot in line with St Helier Hospital's
OL,8,Fantimicrobial guidelines," the coroner
OL,9,Fwrote.
OL,11,FShe added that the drugs did not
OL,12,Fprovide effective coverage against a
OL,13,Fgram positive organism, which was the
OL,14,Fmost likely pathogen causing the
OL,15,Finfection.
OL,17,F"Prior to selecting this combination
OL,18,Fof antibiotics, the surgical team did
OL,19,Fnot consult with the hospital's
OL,20,Fmicrobiology team for advice."
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@ZO]yD@AOU|D@^O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773209293
OL,3,CYoung mother died from sepsis after
OL,4,Cbeing prescribed wrong antibiotics
OL,6,FOn August 16, another drug was given
OL,7,Fto Ms Rochester "which was in line
OL,8,Fwith the hospital guidelines" but she
OL,9,Fdeteriorated and was admitted to
OL,10,Fintensive care on August 17.
OL,12,FBy that time, she was in septic shock
OL,13,Fwith multiple organ failure. There
OL,14,Fwere also signs of infection in her
OL,15,Flungs.
OL,17,F"Despite a maximal antibiotics regime,
OL,18,Fintubation, ventilation and intensive
OL,19,Fmedical support, Ms Rochester
OL,20,Fcontinued to deteriorate," the coroner
OL,21,Fsaid.
OL,26,@oD@QOUpD@]O]yD@AOU|D@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773209293
OL,3,CYoung mother died from sepsis after
OL,4,Cbeing prescribed wrong antibiotics
OL,6,F"She suffered a cardiac arrest in the
OL,7,Fearly hours of the morning on the 19th
OL,8,Fof August, from which she could not be
OL,9,Fresuscitated."
OL,11,FThe coroner ruled that, on August 15,
OL,12,FMs Rochester "should have been, but
OL,13,Fwas not prescribed" the right
OL,14,Fantibiotics and if she had, she most
OL,15,Flikely would have survived.
OL,17,F"Her death was contributed to by
OL,18,Fneglect," she said.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@NO]tD@NOUuD@SO]yD@AOUzD@IO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30609
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773209293
OL,3,CYoung mother died from sepsis after
OL,4,Cbeing prescribed wrong antibiotics
OL,6,FMs Rochester's mother Lorna has
OL,7,Flaunched legal action against the
OL,8,Ftrust.
OL,10,F"Aleisha was the most loving, caring
OL,11,Fand compassionate daughter you could
OL,12,Fwish for," her mother said.
OL,14,F"She was strong, independent and
OL,15,Fambitious, with a vibrant personality
OL,16,Fand had ambitions of starting her own
OL,17,Fbusiness.
OL,19,F"Aleshia was an amazing mummy with
OL,20,Fmotherhood coming to her naturally.
OL,26,@rD@AOUtD@JO]vD@AOU{D@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30610
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773209293
OL,3,CYoung mother died from sepsis after
OL,4,Cbeing prescribed wrong antibiotics
OL,6,F"The bond between Aleisha and Xavier
OL,7,Fwas evident in every moment they spent
OL,8,Ftogether.
OL,10,F"There's still not a day goes by when
OL,11,Fwe don't think of Aleisha or miss
OL,12,Fher...
OL,14,F"There's a huge void in our family and
OL,15,Fthe hardest thing to try and come to
OL,16,Fterms with is how she'll never get to
OL,17,Fsee Xavier grow up and celebrate
OL,18,Fmilestones in life.
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30611
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773209293
OL,3,CYoung mother died from sepsis after
OL,4,Cbeing prescribed wrong antibiotics
OL,6,F"We'll make sure Xavier knows how much
OL,7,Fhis mummy loved him and how proud she
OL,8,Fwould be of him.
OL,10,F"However, I don't think our family
OL,11,Fwill ever get over the pain of losing
OL,12,FAleisha especially in the way we did...
OL,14,F"All we can hope for now is that by
OL,15,Fspeaking out, we can help improve care
OL,16,Ffor others and raise awareness of how
OL,17,Fimportant it is to spot and treat
OL,18,Fsepsis correctly."
OL,26,@nD@AOUrD@AOUvD@AOUzD@RO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30612
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773209293
OL,3,CYoung mother died from sepsis after
OL,4,Cbeing prescribed wrong antibiotics
OL,6,FMadeline Nugent, medical negligence
OL,7,Flawyer at Irwin Mitchell, representing
OL,8,Fthe family, said: "This is a truly
OL,9,Ftragic case which has left Aleisha's
OL,10,Floved ones devastated.
OL,12,F"The neglect finding means the coroner
OL,13,Fwas satisfied that there was a gross
OL,14,Ffailure to provide Aleisha with basic
OL,15,Fmedical care.
OL,17,F"Through our work we continue to see
OL,18,Ftoo many families impacted by sepsis.
OL,26,@pD@SOUtD@AOUyD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30613
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773209293
OL,3,CYoung mother died from sepsis after
OL,4,Cbeing prescribed wrong antibiotics
OL,6,F"While it's too late for Aleisha and
OL,7,Fher family it's now vital that lessons
OL,8,Fare learned from the failings that the
OL,9,Finquest identified in her care."
OL,11,FDr Richard Jennings, group chief
OL,12,Fmedical officer for St George's, Epsom
OL,13,Fand St Helier University Hospitals,
OL,14,Fsaid: "We know we failed Ms Rochester
OL,15,Fby not giving her the correct
OL,16,Fantibiotics, with tragic consequences
OL,17,F` for this we are extremely sorry and
OL,18,Foffer our deepest apologies and
OL,19,Fcondolences to her family.
OL,26,@nD@AOUqD@`O]vD@GOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/14
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,307,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30614
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F306A1773209293
OL,3,CYoung mother died from sepsis after
OL,4,Cbeing prescribed wrong antibiotics
OL,6,F"We sadly can't put this right for Ms
OL,7,FRochester, but we would like to assure
OL,8,Fher family that we have learned from
OL,9,FMs Rochester's death, and we have
OL,10,Ftaken multiple steps to prevent this
OL,11,Fhappening again.
OL,13,F"We are now giving further training to
OL,14,Fstaff on the prompt recognition of
OL,15,Fsepsis, and have taken measures to
OL,16,Fmake sure antibiotic prescribing is
OL,17,Fdone correctly.
OL,19,F"We are also carrying out regular
OL,20,Faudits to make sure our guidelines are
OL,21,Fbeing followed."
OL,26,@nD@AOUuD@AOU{D@AOU}D@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/14
